{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"RemotePlayback.state","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback/state","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>state</code></strong> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback\"><code>RemotePlayback</code></a> interface returns the current state of the <code>RemotePlayback</code> connection.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>One of:</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"connecting\"><code>\"connecting\"</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The user agent is attempting to initiate remote playback with the selected device.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"connected\"><code>\"connected\"</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The transition from local to remote playback has happened. All commands will now take place on the remote device.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"disconnected\"><code>\"disconnected\"</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The remote playback has not been initiated, has failed to initiate, or has been stopped.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In the following example the value of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback/state\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>RemotePlayback.state</code></a> is printed to the console when the user agent successfully connects.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>RemotePlayback<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onconnect</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>RemotePlayback<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/remote-playback/#dom-remoteplayback-state","title":"Remote Playback API"}],"query":"api.RemotePlayback.state"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.RemotePlayback.state","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback/state/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The state read-only property of the RemotePlayback interface returns the current state of the RemotePlayback connection.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:18:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/remoteplayback/state","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/remoteplayback/state/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/e0e09b1df51489867f2e74c18586d168ba5e00d1","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback","title":"RemotePlayback"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback/state","title":"RemotePlayback.state"}],"pageTitle":"RemotePlayback.state - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}